=== G-01-airport: Airport Check-in (A2-B1) ===
Opening: Good morning. May I see your passport and booking reference, please?

[normal check-in]
  IN:  Hi, I'd like to check in for my flight to Tokyo.
  OUT: Good morning. May I see your passport and booking reference, please?

[short answer]
  IN:  Window.
  OUT: A window seat, great choice. Do you have any bags to check in today?

[chinese intent]
  IN:  我想托运一个行李。
  OUT: 可以这样说："I have one suitcase to check." 这句话用来告诉工作人员你有行李需要托运。Do you have any carry-on bags as well?

[off-topic]
  IN:  Can you recommend a good restaurant nearby?
  OUT: Let's focus on the airport check-in practice for now. Do you have your passport and booking reference ready?

[grammar error]
  IN:  I have a reservation name John.
  OUT: Thank you, John. Could I also see your passport and booking reference number, please?
